commit.message:
i386.h (TARGET_DEFAULT): Do not turn on frame pointer elimination in leaf functions by default yet.

        * i386.h (TARGET_DEFAULT): Do not turn on frame pointer
        elimination in leaf functions by default yet.

From-SVN: r54848
